## Acknowledgements

The text-cleanup approach in `lib/textCleanup.js` (fuzzy custom-word
correction, filler-word removal, stutter collapse) and the recording state
machine in `background.js` are JavaScript reimplementations of ideas from
**Handy** by CJ Pais — https://github.com/cjpais/Handy — used under the
MIT License:

    MIT License
    Copyright (c) 2025 CJ Pais

No Handy source code is included in this project; the concepts were ported
from Rust to JavaScript for the browser.
